  "texts": [
    "To ensure the accuracy and reliability of the GT labels in the CXR-AL14 dataset, the intrareader and intrareader variability of the annotation of six experts in the expert group was evaluated.",
    "Since the six experts played the final role in the creation of the CXR-AL14 dataset, we only observed the interreader and intrareader variability among these six experts.",
    "First, 600 CXRs were randomly selected from the CXR-AL14 dataset (excluding the 8000 CXRs for training the preliminary model) and interpreted by the preliminary model.",
    "Then, each radiologist of the twelve radiologists was given 50 CXRs on average for correction (the process is completely consistent with the human-inthe-loop approach).",
    "Finally, we sent the 600 CXRs with corrected annotations to six experts for further correction."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}